locality: Upper slopes of Pianma River, ca. 10 km E of Pianma on the W side of Gaoligong Shan.
Just below the Fengxue Yakou (the pass between Lushui and Pianma), between km 54 and 58, E side of Gaoligong Shan.

Jomolhari. GLORIA site located within the Jigme Dorji Wangchuck National Park. GLORIA BT-JML-SMC. Collaborative collection done by Ugyen Wangchuk Institute for Conservation and Environment (UWICE) and Missouri Botanical Garden (MO). Collectors included: S. Dema, S. Wangmo, J. Wangchuck, Y. Jamtsho, K. Bauer, K. Konchar, & J. Salick.
E Nepal: Sagarmatha Zone, Solukhumbu Distr., Kurke - Pangonba - Kharikhola.
